 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EEscapio connects sophisticated travelers with distinctive hotels. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAt Escapio, we are dedicated to making it as simple as possible to find a distinctive hotel that meets your needs. We have created a portal that enables you to find satisfying results quickly and easily, or take your time and enjoy the sights. Escapio comes from \u0026#8220;escape\u0026#8221;: Refuge, getting away from it all, from the myriad of overlapping offers and demands of everyday life. Intelligent search parameters provide rapid access for travelers who know what they\u00e2\u20ac\u2122re looking for. We have analyzed the needs and wishes of sophisticated travelers and offer a new kind of online search: Travel topics such as Gourmet, Design, Wellness, hotel types such as romantic hotels, spa hotels, regions such as Tuscany, Bavaria and the Andalusia and seasonal events such as vintage or classic festivals Targeted, efficient searches are as easy as \u0026#8220;surfing\u0026#8221; and exploring the numerous offers.\u003C/p\u003E",
